The '''Plains of Harkul''',  or simply '''Harkul''', was a desert plain located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kuar]]. [[Mandalore the Indomitable]] and [[Ulic Qel-Droma/Legends|Ulic Qel-Droma]] [[Duel on Kuar|dueled]] there during the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]].

